  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> September 20, 2025</p>
  <p>
    CGI Buzz Studio (“we”, “our”, or “us”) respects your privacy. 
    This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use <em>Fate of Antara</em> 
    (the “Game”).
  </p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Account Data:</strong> If you create an account using PlayFab or Steam, we may collect your username, unique user ID, and linked email (if provided by the platform).</li>
    <li><strong>Game Progress:</strong> Saved progress, achievements, and virtual currency balances are stored using PlayFab’s secure services.</li>
    <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> We may use aggregated and anonymous gameplay data (e.g., missions completed, levels unlocked) to improve the game.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
  <p>Your information is used only for:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Saving and syncing your game progress</li>
    <li>Enabling in-game purchases and rewards</li>
    <li>Improving stability, balance, and features of the game</li>
    <li>Providing technical support</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Sharing of Information</h2>
  <p>
    We do not sell your personal information. Data may be shared with trusted third-party providers only to operate the game, such as:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>PlayFab (Microsoft Azure)</strong> – for account, cloud saves, and virtual currency</li>
    <li><strong>Steam</strong> – for achievements, in-game purchases, and cloud saves</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    Our game is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children. 
    If you believe we have unintentionally collected such data, please contact us and we will delete it.
  </p>

  <h2>Security</h2>
  <p>
    We take appropriate measures to protect your data. However, no system is 100% secure. We encourage you to use strong passwords and keep your accounts safe.
  </p>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <p>
    Depending on your location, you may have the right to access, update, or request deletion of your personal data. 
    To make a request, please contact us at the email below.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. Updates will be posted on this page with a revised effective date.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:  
    <strong>Email:</strong> support@cgibuzzstudio.com
  </p>

